Gaupol 0.21
===========

 [X] Restore inline spell-check, replace the previous GtkSpell
     dependency with a dependency on pygtkspellcheck
     * http://koehlma.github.com/projects/pygtkspellcheck.html
 [X] Add partial support for fancy Unicode dashes, ellipses and
     quotation marks in text correction patterns and "Toggle dialogue
     dashes" action
 [X] Fix search dialog mnemonics
 [X] Apply GNOME Goal: Remove markup in translatable messages

Gaupol 1.0
==========

 * Add a built-in GStreamer-based video player
 * Add a GStreamer-based audio waveform display
 * https://live.gnome.org/GnomeGoals/PortToGtkApplication
 * https://live.gnome.org/GnomeGoals/PortToGMenu
